  <brief_title>Evaluating Clinical Outcomes of Targeted Radiofrequency Ablation and Kyphoplasty (Also Known as Vertebral Augmentation) to Treat Painful Metastatic Vertebral Body Tumors</brief_title>
  <acronym>EU-STAR</acronym>
